== 獎項記錄 ==
該片入圍[[第62届奥斯卡金像奖|第62届奥斯卡金像奖]]的3項大獎，拿下其中的[[奥斯卡最佳音效剪辑奖|最佳音效剪輯獎]]<ref name="Oscars1990">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1990 |title=The 62nd Academy Awards (1990) Nominees and Winners |publisher=Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences |website=oscars.org |accessdate=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2015-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402002952/http://www.oscars.org/oscars/ceremonies/1990 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並榮獲[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳戲劇片。

